        <item>
            <title>中國八寶粥：可當小米鏡頭蓋配件，整埋「小米 14 Ultra 專業攝影套裝」夠識玩 </title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/16/xiaomi-14-ultra-camera-cover/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xiaomi-14-ultra-camera-cover</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/16/xiaomi-14-ultra-camera-cover/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 07:55:57 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1224757</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中國一個八寶粥品牌銀鷺，旗下的罐裝甜品的蓋掩，被指可當成小米 14 Ultra 相機的鏡頭蓋。銀鷺網路小編馬上出招，呼籲小米用家一定要用八寶粥蓋子當成小米鏡頭蓋，並稱他們的蓋子是「嚴絲無縫、完美適配（編輯按：合襯）」。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224758" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f5abb08595f3c6e1-694x553.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="553" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f5abb08595f3c6e1-694x553.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f5abb08595f3c6e1.jpg 1129w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Xiaomi 14 Ultra 背面相機頗為巨大，建有 Leica Summilux 四鏡頭模組，並採用 5000 萬像素 1 吋感光元件，附有 F1.63~F4 無段可變光圈，其他鏡頭都支援 5000 萬像素高解像度攝影。有網民發現，中國食品品牌銀鷺旗下八寶粥產品的蓋子，剛好可貼合這個龐大突出的相機模組。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/30e9a65f382d0bd-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/30e9a65f382d0bd-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/30e9a65f382d0bd-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>銀鷺的網路小編馬上發揮創意，更加將八寶粥蓋子拿到小米專門店拍攝了一輯相片。在經過該小編實測後，證明蓋子「嚴絲無縫」，完美地蓋在 Xiaomi 14 Ultra 的鏡頭組之上。網民指以後也不用擔心跌爛相機鏡頭了。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/tech/1422816.htm">CNBETA</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/30/redmi-buds-5-pro-review/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Redmi Buds 5 Pro　外形　佩戴感　功能　音質開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/16/xiaomi-might-launch-an-8-inch-tablet/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">多名高層微博爆料，小米 8 吋平板料短期發表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/07/mi14-mi14ultra-hk-price-revealed/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【報價】小米 14 + 小米 14 Ultra 港行正式推出	首「賣大包」送攝影套裝 + 抵玩定價公佈</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/16/xiaomi-14-ultra-camera-cover/mobile-phone/">中國八寶粥：可當小米鏡頭蓋配件，整埋「小米 14 Ultra 專業攝影套裝」夠識玩 </a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
